{"lemma":"بَلْقَعِ","slug":"بَلْقَعِ","root":"ب.ل.ق.ع","root_slug":"ب-ل-ق-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ب-ل-ق-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n3264","n3266"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A8%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n3264","headword_ar":"بَلْقَعَ","root":"blqE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEapN","text_ar":"بَلْقَعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a country, or region,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void; destitute of herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage, and of human beings, &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n3266","headword_ar":"بَلْقَعٌ","root":"blqE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEapN","text_ar":"بَلْقَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A land that is vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void; destitute of herbage"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage, and of human beings, &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is nothing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or the former signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) [or instead of using the former alone, you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN baloqaEN","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ بَلْقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for] you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manozilN","text_ar":"مَنْزِلٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEN","text_ar":"بَلْقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, place of alighting"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abiding"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daArN baloqaEN","text_ar":"دَارٌ بَلْقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, house"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", when it is an epithet, (S, TA,) applied to a mase. subst. and to a fem.; (TA;) but if it be a subst., you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinotahayonaA A_ilaY","text_ar":"اِنْتَهَيْنَا اـِلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"malosaA='a","text_ar":"مَلْسَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEapK","text_ar":"بَلْقَعَةٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we came at last to a smooth, vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, land"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEapN","text_ar":"بَلْقَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a land in which are no trees, either in sands or in plain or level tracts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vacant land, in which is no one, whether there be in it herbage or not, and whether plain or not:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 445:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"balaAqiEu","text_ar":"بَلَاقِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Mgh, K.) It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyamiynu AlfaAjirapu ta*aru","text_ar":"اليَمِينُ الفَاجِرَةُ تَذَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, TA; but in the second and third of these, in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*aru","text_ar":"تَذَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", we find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tadaEu","text_ar":"تَدَعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The false oath causes the places of abode to become void,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vacant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e., by reason of its evil influence, the possessions and their possessors perish; (Mgh;) or the [false] swearer becomes poor, and the property that was in his house goes away; (Sh;) or God renders him in a state of disunion, and changes the blessings which He had conferred upon him: (TA:) accord. to another relation, the words of the trad. are"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alyamiynu Algamuwsu Alx","text_ar":"اليَمِينُ الغَمُوسُ الخ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diyaArN baloqaEN","text_ar":"دِيَارٌ بَلْقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vacant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"void, places of abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as though the places were one place: (TA:) and Ru-beh says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"faA^aSobaHato daArahumu balaAqiEaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And their abode became vacant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) and it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHati AlA^aroDu balaAqiEa","text_ar":"اَصْبَحَتِ الاَرْضُ بَلَاقِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the land became altogether vacant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; the pl. being used to render the meaning intensive, as in the phrases"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDN sabaAsibu","text_ar":"اَرْضٌ سَبَاسِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vawobN A^axolaAqN","text_ar":"ثَوْبٌ اَخْلَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IAth, TA;) or because every portion thereof is considered as being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blqE","text_ar":"بلقع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓ with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)  A woman"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"devoid of every good quality."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b3-  IF says that the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"l","text_ar":"ل"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baloqaEN","text_ar":"بَلْقَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is augmentative. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}